snippet.title: Amber Rose Wins Most Likely to Steal Your Girl At First-Ever All Def Movie Awards!
snippet.description:
Subscribe our Channel 

Amber Rose is all smiles while arriving at the 2016 All Def Movie Awards held at Lure Nightclub on Wednesday (February 24) in Hollywood, Calif.

The 32-year-old model was joined by Michael Ealy, Cassie, Ice Cube and his son O’Shea Jackson Jr., Sanaa Lathan, Karrueche Tran, Bill Bellamy, Eva Marcille, Nick Cannon, Snoop Dogg, and Marlon Wayans at the event, which was created by All Def Digital’s Russell Simmons in response to the “stunning lack of diversity” in Hollywood.

PHOTOS: Check out the latest pics of Amber Rose

Sanaa took home Best Actress for her role in The Perfect Guy, Ice and O’Shea picked up Best Picture for Straight Outta Compton, and Amber won the Most Likely to Steal Your Girl Award.

Amber just teamed up with Zoobe to create a 3D character and her fans will be able to customize her character into their own alter ego to express themselves and communicate as Amber in the digital world. Get the app now.

25+ pictures inside of Amber Rose, Michael Ealy and others at the ceremony
